AI_EOTrainingDataset.name: Airound-aerial
AI_EOTrainingDataset.description: AiRound is composed of 11,753 images distributed among 11 classes, including: airport, bridge, church, forest, lake, river, skyscraper, stadium, statue, tower, and urban park.\r\nEach sample is composed by a triplet, that contains images in 3 distinct points of view: (i) a ground perspective image; (ii) a high resolution RGB aerial image; and (iii) a multi-spectral image taken from the Sentinel-2 satellite.\r\nAll images are paired and were manually checked to guarantee their correctness.
